  "rationale": "The Home Hero section is designed using Finsweet's 6-layer hierarchy to ensure consistent spacing and scalability. A Flexbox layout is used for the main component to achieve pixel-perfect alignment between the content and the illustration. Units are 100% 'rem' for accessibility and fluid responsiveness. Custom classes (e.g., home-hero_image) are used for specific elements, while utility classes (e.g., heading-style-h1, padding-global) maintain global consistency. The section starts with a top padding of 5.75rem to account for the fixed navbar (as defined in MAS-V2-002), ensuring content starts immediately below it. Spacing wrappers (margin-bottom) are used to handle vertical gaps between text elements, adhering to Client-First best practices."
